des: Good Morning Gwinnett is broadcast live Monday- Wednesday at 10am and on Thursday at 11am. The podcast is hosted by Audrey Bell-Kearney and is the official Gwinnett County Podcast all about people and place around Gwinnett County Georgia. Learn about what's happening in politics, Gwinnett living, Gwinnett business, Gwinnett job force. Also be entertained with daily horoscopes and music between the segments. If you are looking for a non-profit to support be sure to listen to the People Helping People segment where Audrey gives a shout out to a local non-profit that are doing great things in the community and surrounding communities. This podcast is made possible by Noise Media Network.
